   Canada How to Contact the Canadian Competition Bureau

   The following information will allow you to contact the Competition
   Bureau at Industry Canada directly:

   Internet Websites:

     www.competition.ic.gc.ca (English)

     www.concurrence.ic.gc.ca (French)

   Telephonic Inquiries:

     1-800-348-5358 (toll free in Canada)

     1-819-997-4282 (outside of Canada)

   Fax Inquiries:

     1-819-997-0324

   E-Mail Inquiries:

     compbureau@ic.gc.ca (English)

     burconcurrence@ic.gc.ca (French)


